      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.orbital.p.21",
      "en": "Deploy Orbital servers directly in your own data center for maximum control, security, and compliance requirements.",
      "it": "",
      "fr": "",
      "source": "orbital.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.orbital.p.22",
      "en": "Deploy Orbital servers in professional colocation facilities with redundant power, cooling, and connectivity while maintaining on-premise control.",
      "it": "",
      "fr": "",
      "source": "orbital.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.orbital.p.23",
      "en": "Keep your data within your own infrastructure, ensuring complete control over sensitive information and compliance with data protection regulations.",
      "it": "",
      "fr": "",
      "source": "orbital.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.orbital.p.24",
      "en": "Eliminate network latency and bandwidth limitations by running your workloads directly on your premises with local data access.",
      "it": "",
      "fr": "",
      "source": "orbital.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.orbital.p.25",
      "en": "Maintain complete control over your security posture and meet strict compliance requirements for regulated industries.",
      "it": "",
      "fr": "",
      "source": "orbital.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.orbital.p.26",
      "en": "Fixed hardware costs with no variable cloud pricing, making it easier to budget and plan for long-term infrastructure investments.",
      "it": "",
      "fr": "",
      "source": "orbital.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.orbital.p.27",
      "en": "Common questions about Orbital servers and deployment",
      "it": "",
      "fr": "",
      "source": "orbital.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.orbital.p.28",
      "en": "Each Orbital server includes the hardware, AtomOS pre-installed with perpetual licensing, and comprehensive support. No additional software licensing required.",
      "it": "",
      "fr": "",
      "source": "orbital.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.orbital.p.29",
      "en": "Yes, Orbital servers are designed exclusively for on-premise deployment in your own data center or colocation facilities. This ensures maximum control, security, and compliance.",
      "it": "",
      "fr": "",
      "source": "orbital.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.orbital.p.3",
      "en": "Deploy exclusively in your own data center or colocation facility for complete control and data sovereignty",
      "it": "",
      "fr": "",
      "source": "orbital.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.orbital.p.30",
      "en": "Yes, we offer custom configurations through our Orbital Custom option. Our team will work with you to design the perfect solution for your specific requirements.",
      "it": "",
      "fr": "",
      "source": "orbital.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.orbital.p.31",
      "en": "All Orbital servers include comprehensive hardware and software support, remote management capabilities, and access to our technical team.",
      "it": "",
      "fr": "",
      "source": "orbital.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.orbital.p.32",
      "en": "AtomOS perpetual licensing means you own the software license forever with no recurring fees. Updates and support are included for the life of the server.",
      "it": "",
      "fr": "",
      "source": "orbital.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.orbital.p.33",
      "en": "On-premise deployment provides data sovereignty, eliminates latency, ensures compliance, and offers predictable costs with no variable cloud pricing.",
      "it": "",
      "fr": "",
      "source": "orbital.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
